text: Fear factor may refer to: *Fear Factor, an American television show that was broadcast on NBC from 2001 to 2006 and 2011 to 2012 *Fear Factor (Yu-Gi-Oh! GX episode), an episode of Yu-Gi-Oh! GX *Pinoy Fear Factor, a Filipino television show that was broadcast on ABS-CBN from 2008 through 2009 *Fear Factor Chile, a Chilean television show that was broadcast on Canal 13 from 2010 *Fear Factor Malaysia, a Malaysian television show that was broadcast on Astro Ria and Astro Maya HD from 2013 ==See also== * Fear Factory, an American rock/metal band
title: Fear factor (disambiguation)
